com.github.acquized.retile.reports

Class Report

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.acquized.retile.reports.Report

  • public class Report
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a unique Report made by a User regarding any other User. The Class consists of following variables:
    • token - Represents the Unique ID Token for a Report (a report can have multiple Report Objects assigned to it
    • reporter - Represents the Player that reported the victim
    • victim - Represents the Player that got reported by the reporter
    • reason - Represents the Reason why the victim got reported by the reporter
    • timestamp - Represents the Time and Date where the Player got reported. This is in milliseconds.
